item.title: Oahu, Hawai'i
item.description: The trip that started it all… I had no intentions of traveling to Hawaii. I was trying to get to Canada to go on a fishing trip. After my flights fell a part, I wasn’t going to be able to make it in time to meet up with my family to get to Canada.
